Synchrony call
    if (req.url = '/'){
            page = fs.readFileSync('index.html');
        }

Asynchronous call
    fs.readFile('index.html', function(err, page){
            if (err) {
                console.error(err);
                res.statusCode = 500;
                res.end('Server error occurred!');
                return;
            }
            res.end(page);
        });

What, where is using.

LibUV - library cross platform function realization